'''''Star Wars Kids'' 7''' is the seventh issue of [[Star Wars Kids (1997)|''Star Wars Kids'']] magazine. It was published by [[Scholastic]] and released in [[March]] [[1998]]. Issue 7 included part two of the serial [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] ''[[X-Wing Marks the Spot]]'', written by [[Mike W. Barr]].

''Star Wars Kids'' 7 was available exclusively to subscribers of Scholastic's ''[[Star Wars Missions]]'' young-reader series and [[roleplaying game]], which arrived as monthly continuity packages via direct mail. Each package included a new ''Star Wars Kids'' magazine issue and the latest ''Star Wars Missions'' adventure book. ''Star Wars Kids'' 7 came packaged with the game's seventh adventure book, [[Star Wars Missions 7: Ithorian Invasion|''Ithorian Invasion'']].

